Hentikan.

8
00:02:37,859 --> 00:02:41,228
Kau menyakiti kami.

9
00:02:41,261 --> 00:02:43,230
Terbakarlah di neraka.

10
00:03:02,950 --> 00:03:04,852
Tidak...

11
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:25,272
Apa yang kau lakukan, Yosille?

12
00:03:26,708 --> 00:03:29,443
Kau tahu akibatnya jika
